    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies an optional OSPF protocol extension to represent router metrics in a multi-access network in two parts: the metric from the router to the network and the metric from the network to the router.  For such networks, the router-to-router metric for OSPF route computation is the sum of the two parts.  This document updates RFC 2328.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
